#Orcish Squatters (#1085) - PARKED, REAL PARTIAL BUG:
#  - The may-steal leg WORKS: accept (choice 0 + pads) at the COMBATDAMAGE step,
#    then pads + land click + pads - the land changes controller. (At blockers the
#    @combat(notblocked) trigger has not fired yet; no prompt.)
#  - The 'assigns no combat damage' leg (&& fog from(this) ueot) NEVER works: the
#    trigger fires during the damage step AFTER combat damage is assigned, so the
#    fog arrives too late and the opponent still takes 2.
#  - Engine-round item: @combat(notblocked) needs to fire before damage assignment
#    (or the fog needs to apply retroactively) for cards in this family.
#Working steal sequence for re-enlistment once fixed:
[INIT]
firstmain
[PLAYER1]
inplay:orcish squatters
[PLAYER2]
inplay:darksteel citadel
[DO]
goto attackers
orcish squatters
next
goto combatdamage
goto combatdamage
choice 0
goto combatdamage
goto combatdamage
darksteel citadel
goto combatdamage
goto combatdamage
goto end
goto end
[ASSERT]
ENDOFTURN
[PLAYER1]
inplay:orcish squatters,darksteel citadel
[PLAYER2]
life:20
[END]
